	<div data-role="content">
		<p>I was getting some great shots of Jay Alvarrez when he started talking to me about cameras. He offered to take some shots for me from the center of the park. He introduced me to Andre, who's riding style is one of the cleanest I've seen up close. Our research indicates much of the rides looked awesome.</p>
